http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#lab.value: List of the first women holders of political offices in Asia

http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#com.value: This is a list of political offices which have been held by a woman, with details of the first woman holder of each office. It is ordered by the countries in Asia and by dates of appointment. Please observe that this list is meant to contain only the first woman to hold of a political office, and not all the female holders of that office.
